Add a "New Level" button to the LevelStack component so users can create levels from the UI (F-025 improvement — currently only existing level elevation editing works; level creation requires the AI chat).

**Background:**
- Backend `createLevel` command: `{ type: 'createLevel', id: string, name: string, elevationMm: number, alsoCreatePlanView: true }` — also auto-creates a plan view for the new level
- The `onSemanticCommand` prop in WorkspaceLeftRail handles all commands
- LevelStack receives sorted `levels` array — the last item has the highest elevation

